930
01:11:11,133 --> 01:11:14,100
Giorgos alias George Karalis.

931
01:11:14,900 --> 01:11:16,833
Dia di penjara 6 bulan di Pentonville.

932
01:11:17,066 --> 01:11:19,466
Sebelumnya dia di Belgia

933
01:11:19,466 --> 01:11:21,666
karena pencurian dan penyeludupan berlian.

934
01:11:31,900 --> 01:11:33,066
Menarik.

935
01:11:38,333 --> 01:11:41,300
Kuingin bicara dengan
Kepala Inspektur, Greenfield.

936
01:11:42,266 --> 01:11:44,200
Peralatan kita telah rusak.

937
01:11:51,166 --> 01:11:52,300
Terima kasih banyak, pak.

938
01:11:52,300 --> 01:11:53,866
Semoga penerbangannya lancar.
/ Terima kasih.

939
01:12:00,133 --> 01:12:00,933
Ludo,

940
01:12:01,733 --> 01:12:03,800
kau tahu aku tak mempermainkan keluarga,
ngerti?

941
01:12:03,933 --> 01:12:05,900
Kau ingat aku telah mengenalmu

942
01:12:05,900 --> 01:12:07,466
sejak usiamu 10 tahun.

943
01:12:07,466 --> 01:12:09,566
Nyalakan musiknya.
/ Kita bisa bicarakan ini.

944
01:12:12,133 --> 01:12:15,100
c, kau sinting, keparat!

945
01:12:15,366 --> 01:12:17,600
Jangan begini terhadapku.

946
01:12:19,066 --> 01:12:19,866
Ludo!

947
01:12:36,490 --> 01:12:37,490
Sial.

948
01:12:41,414 --> 01:12:42,414
Mundur!

949
01:12:47,766 --> 01:12:49,100
Maju! Salip!

950
01:12:59,866 --> 01:13:00,666
Ayo,

951
01:13:01,390 --> 01:13:02,765
keluar!

952
01:13:04,489 --> 01:13:06,489
Kau!

953
01:13:09,313 --> 01:13:11,313
Sialan! Awas!

954
01:13:26,300 --> 01:13:27,100
Sial.

955
01:13:40,400 --> 01:13:41,500
Apa kabar, bro?

956
01:13:44,400 --> 01:13:45,133
Hey, kalian.

957
01:13:45,133 --> 01:13:46,166
Aku senang ketemu kalian.

958
01:13:50,200 --> 01:13:51,400
Dengar.

959
01:13:51,500 --> 01:13:52,300
maafkan aku, ya.

960
01:13:52,300 --> 01:13:54,800
Mereka menjebakku,
supaya bisa ngambil berliannya.

961
01:13:56,533 --> 01:13:57,566
Brengsek!

962
01:13:57,590 --> 01:13:58,665
Brengsek kau!

963
01:13:58,666 --> 01:13:59,766
Dengarkan aku,

964
01:13:59,766 --> 01:14:00,866
tolol!

965
01:14:01,566 --> 01:14:05,400
Dengarkan aku! Aku tak bawa apa-apa.

966
01:14:05,400 --> 01:14:07,300
Menurutmu apa yang akan terjadi.

967
01:14:07,324 --> 01:14:09,324
Dengar.

968
01:15:09,300 --> 01:15:10,100
Ketemu kau.

969
01:15:10,666 --> 01:15:12,733
Kepada semua bandara internasional,
stasiun kereta api...

970
01:15:12,733 --> 01:15:14,566
dan laporkan ke petugas paspor.

971
01:15:14,566 --> 01:15:15,566
Giorgos Karalis, pria kulit putih, 30 tahunan,

972
01:15:15,566 --> 01:15:18,066
dia bepergian dengan paspor Malta
atau Afrika Selatan,

973
01:15:18,100 --> 01:15:19,800
segeralah ditangkap.

974
01:15:49,766 --> 01:15:51,800
Hai. Mackenzie 229.

975
01:15:51,800 --> 01:15:53,633
Sayangnya aku kelupaan kunciku.

976
01:15:53,700 --> 01:15:55,500
Baik,

977
01:15:55,500 --> 01:15:57,700
Tn. Mackenzie, kau punya kartu identitas?

978
01:15:57,700 --> 01:15:58,166
Ah, yeah

979
01:15:58,166 --> 01:15:59,200
ada di kamarku.

980
01:16:20,666 --> 01:16:23,466
Hai Kopral. Asisten Komisaris Palmer.
/ Senang bertemu denganmu.

981
01:16:36,133 --> 01:16:37,066
Hai.
/ Hai.

982
01:16:37,066 --> 01:16:39,800
Bisa pesan tiket penerbangan pertamaku
yang ke Marakes?

983
01:16:39,800 --> 01:16:41,666
Pasporku ada disini.

984
01:16:44,966 --> 01:16:46,766
Aku dia punya...

985
01:16:48,733 --> 01:16:52,266
dia punya masalah psikologis.
/ PTSD?

986
01:16:52,300 --> 01:16:54,366
Ya, mungkin...

987
01:16:55,066 --> 01:16:56,200
kekecewaan.

988
01:16:56,866 --> 01:16:59,466
Rupanya, dia mengajukan diri
untuk tinggal di Afghanistan.

989
01:17:00,500 --> 01:17:03,766
Teman-temannya di brigade bilang
dia sangat menginginkan ini.

990
01:17:05,366 --> 01:17:06,633
Kau kenal orang ini?

991
01:17:08,866 --> 01:17:10,700
Tidak, belum pernah lihat dia.

992
01:17:12,266 --> 01:17:14,666
Tapi dia, aku kenal...

993
01:17:15,390 --> 01:17:17,390
Rahim.

994
01:17:17,900 --> 01:17:20,100
Dia dulu penerjemah untuk Mayor Tranter.

995
01:17:20,700 --> 01:17:23,266
Mayor yang membawa dia dan keluarganya ke sini

996
01:17:23,266 --> 01:17:25,800
demi keselamatan.
Kusering lihat dia diberbagai acara.

997
01:17:26,200 --> 01:17:28,266
Semua jalan menuju Afghanistan.

998
01:17:29,666 --> 01:17:33,166
Karalis setahun bekerja di sana,
untuk penambangan batu permata.

999
01:17:34,600 --> 01:17:37,066
Clareese, utus staf perbatasan Inggris
untuk menanyai

1000
01:17:37,066 --> 01:17:38,766
Mayor Tranta dan Rahim Kadedadza.

1001
01:17:38,766 --> 01:17:39,566
Ya, bu.

1002
01:17:57,933 --> 01:18:00,633
Karalis, di Heathrow.
Dia pesan penerbangan ke Marakes.

1003
01:18:41,600 --> 01:18:44,066
<i>Mohon perhatian, para penumpang Air Turkey
menuju ke Istanbul.</i>

1004
01:18:44,066 --> 01:18:45,000
Paspor.

1005
01:18:45,466 --> 01:18:46,266
Yeah.

1006
01:18:46,566 --> 01:18:47,366
Ini pasporku.

1007
01:19:01,333 --> 01:19:03,600
Selamat menikmati penerbangannya, Tn. Melville.
/ Terima kasih.

1008
01:19:08,566 --> 01:19:10,833
Karalis tak ada di penerbangan Marakes.

1009
01:19:10,866 --> 01:19:13,100
<i>Dia check-in, lalu menghilang.</i>
/ Baik.

1010
01:19:13,100 --> 01:19:16,066
Dan tebak siapa petugas jaga malam
yang betugas di lokasi bom?

1011
01:19:18,133 --> 01:19:19,633
Payam Kadedadza,

1012
01:19:19,933 --> 01:19:22,266
kakaknya Rahim.
/ Terus selidiki itu.

1013
01:19:22,333 --> 01:19:24,633
Kami sampai di rumahnya Mayor Tranter.

1014
01:19:28,066 --> 01:19:28,866
Polisi!
/ Polisi!

1015
01:19:29,766 --> 01:19:30,566
Polisi!

1016
01:19:32,366 --> 01:19:34,266
Aman.
/ Bu.

1017
01:19:59,290 --> 01:20:01,790
[6 TEWAS DALAM SERANGAN ROKET]

1018
01:20:06,314 --> 01:20:08,314
[KEKACAUAN TANPA AKHIR DI AFGHANISTAN]

1019
01:20:08,315 --> 01:20:11,215
[KESALAHAN FATAL, PENYERANGAN TERHADAP KORPS
LOGISTIK KERAJAAN, 3 TEWAS, 7 TERLUKA]

1020
01:20:23,439 --> 01:20:29,439
<font color="#00ffff">--Markas138--</font>

1021
01:20:34,463 --> 01:20:36,463
BÜYÜK VARAN 2
ISTANBUL

1022
01:21:04,966 --> 01:21:06,700
Bommu meledak terlalu cepat.

1023
01:21:08,733 --> 01:21:10,866
Polisi memburumu
kayak wabah.

1024
01:21:11,366 --> 01:21:12,766
Aku harus mengambil keputusan.

1025
01:21:12,766 --> 01:21:14,000
Kau membuat keputusan yang bagus.

1026
01:21:15,300 --> 01:21:16,366
Terima kasih.

1027
01:21:18,466 --> 01:21:19,766
Kita mendapat yang dicari.

1028
01:21:20,933 --> 01:21:22,300
Kurasa begitu.

1029
01:21:23,500 --> 01:21:24,300
Ya.

1030
01:21:25,533 --> 01:21:26,866
Kenapa tanganmu?

1031
01:21:27,900 --> 01:21:30,466
Masalah makin runyam.

1032
01:21:32,000 --> 01:21:33,700
Tapi aku berhutang nyawa padamu, kawan.

1033
01:21:37,466 --> 01:21:38,300
Sudahlah.

1034
01:21:42,600 --> 01:21:44,500
Lalu apa rencanamu selanjutnya, huh?

1035
01:21:47,333 --> 01:21:48,400
Ada yang mengganggu pikiranku.

1036
01:21:50,366 --> 01:21:51,800
Mau bereskan beberapa hal.

1037
01:21:56,500 --> 01:21:57,866
Mungkin kita nanti kerjasama lagi.

1038
01:21:58,533 --> 01:21:59,966
Apa kau sudah gila?

1039
01:22:01,300 --> 01:22:02,100
Mungkin.

1040
01:22:16,166 --> 01:22:17,400
Asalamualaikum.
/ Salam.

1041
01:22:17,424 --> 01:22:19,424
Kau tak apa-apa?

1042
01:22:21,133 --> 01:22:22,000
Syukurlah.

1043
01:22:23,266 --> 01:22:24,266
Kita siap?

1044
01:22:25,400 --> 01:22:27,400
Ya.
/ Yuk, kerjakan.

1045
01:22:57,266 --> 01:22:59,766
Harga terbaik kami.
Semuanya.

1046
01:23:05,866 --> 01:23:08,100
Kayaknya ada kesalahpahaman, tuan-tuan.

1047
01:23:08,600 --> 01:23:09,966
Kami berbisnis ke tempat lain saja.

1048
01:23:11,533 --> 01:23:13,066
Oke, oke, tolong tunggu.

1049
01:23:42,566 --> 01:23:43,366
Oke.

1050
01:23:45,700 --> 01:23:46,500
Kita sepakat?

1051
01:23:47,900 --> 01:23:48,700
Sepakat.

1052
01:23:49,166 --> 01:23:50,033
Katakan kapan.

1053
01:23:51,100 --> 01:23:51,900
Kapan?

1054
01:23:55,500 --> 01:23:57,000
Terkonfirmasi. Beres.

1055
01:24:00,533 --> 01:24:01,800
Memang beres.

1056
01:24:03,300 --> 01:24:05,066
Terima kasih.
/ Terima kasih.

1057
01:24:13,533 --> 01:24:14,433
Kita bagi rata.

1058
01:24:28,066 --> 01:24:28,866
Bagus.

1059
01:24:34,433 --> 01:24:35,433
Kita pergi sekarang.

1060
01:24:39,066 --> 01:24:40,166
Oh, maaf.

1061
01:24:42,500 --> 01:24:43,300
Semoga beruntung.

1062
01:24:50,700 --> 01:24:51,600
Selamat tinggal, teman.

1063
01:25:23,133 --> 01:25:25,300
Sialan kau, enyah kalian!

1064
01:25:27,366 --> 01:25:29,800
Naik ke mobil!

1065
01:25:32,300 --> 01:25:34,466
Kalian, dengarkan aku.

1066
01:25:34,566 --> 01:25:36,133
Aku punya uang, dengar?

1067
01:25:36,133 --> 01:25:38,800
Aku punya uang, bisa kubayar kalian.
/ Diam!

1068
01:25:38,800 --> 01:25:42,266
Aku bisa bayar.
Dengar... sialan.

1069
01:25:42,290 --> 01:25:43,290
Brengsek!

1070
01:25:45,414 --> 01:25:48,314
10 TAHUN SEBELUMNYA

1071
01:25:55,438 --> 01:25:59,438
Jika kita singkirkan bom-bom itu,
kita bisa tahu pergerakan musuh.

1072
01:26:00,500 --> 01:26:03,066
Akan kuupayakan sebisanya
untuk membersihkan area ini.

1073
01:26:03,390 --> 01:26:05,390
Sampaikan salam kami pada kapten.

1074
01:26:06,300 --> 01:26:08,200
Salamualaikum.
/ Salamualaikum.

1075
01:26:08,466 --> 01:26:10,366
Bagaimana mengucapkan "dimana"?
/ Ҫirta.

1076
01:26:10,390 --> 01:26:13,490
Ҫirta. Ҫirta tor gar.
/ Ya.

1077
01:26:13,700 --> 01:26:14,633
Bagus.

1078
01:26:18,066 --> 01:26:19,500
Gawat. Ayo.

1079
01:26:20,066 --> 01:26:21,433
Sembunyi sekarang.

1080
01:26:23,733 --> 01:26:24,600
Hey, berhenti. Jangan bergerak.

1081
01:26:24,600 --> 01:26:27,666
Kau menginjak ranjau darat.

1082
01:26:37,966 --> 01:26:38,966
Sial.

1083
01:26:38,990 --> 01:26:40,990
Tempat ini penuh bom rakitan. (IED)

1084
01:26:42,366 --> 01:26:43,166
Apa?

1085
01:26:44,500 --> 01:26:46,266
Siapa mereka?

1086
01:26:59,490 --> 01:27:00,490
Sial!

1087
01:27:10,666 --> 01:27:12,566
Berhenti! Lihat aku!

1088
01:27:12,566 --> 01:27:15,266
Diam di situ, jangan bergerak.
Kita dikepung bom rakitan.

1089
01:27:15,266 --> 01:27:17,233
Siapa kau?
Sedang apa disini?

1090
01:27:18,733 --> 01:27:20,300
Aku kerja di penambangan
batu permata.

1091
01:27:20,300 --> 01:27:21,200
Mengapa kau diikat?

1092
01:27:21,200 --> 01:27:23,033
Bosku mau membunuhku.

1093
01:27:23,166 --> 01:27:24,433
Pengawalnya yang menyerahkanku padanya.

1094
01:27:24,457 --> 01:27:26,332
Akan kubantu, kau harus membantuku.

1095
01:27:26,356 --> 01:27:28,356
Aku membantumu, kau bantu aku.

1096
01:27:29,466 --> 01:27:30,700
Semoga aku tak menyesali ini.

1097
01:27:32,433 --> 01:27:34,166
Hey, ikuti petunjuk ini.

1098
01:27:34,666 --> 01:27:36,166
Kitari ke belakang gunung itu,

1099
01:27:36,166 --> 01:27:37,466
dan carilah tabung bom besar.

1100
01:27:37,467 --> 01:27:38,701
Kenapa tak kau sendiri saja?

1101
01:27:39,200 --> 01:27:40,900
Kakiku terjebak di ranjau darat.

1102
01:27:41,000 --> 01:27:42,366
Kalau kuangkat, kita semua mati.

1103
01:27:42,390 --> 01:27:43,365
Baik, aku paham.
/ Siapa namamu?

1104
01:27:43,366 --> 01:27:45,300
Namaku Karalis.
/ Karalis.

1105
01:27:45,400 --> 01:27:48,300
Ikuti kabel ini,
kita harus netralkan bom rakitannya.

1106
01:27:48,300 --> 01:27:49,333
Mengerti?

1107
01:27:49,333 --> 01:27:50,100
Tidak ngerti.

1108
01:27:50,100 --> 01:27:52,166
Pada hitungan ke-3, aku akan melindungimu.
Paham?

1109
01:27:52,166 --> 01:27:53,800
1 2 3.

1110
01:27:58,266 --> 01:27:59,633
Sialan!

1111
01:28:01,000 --> 01:28:02,066
Rahim.
/ Ya?

1112
01:28:02,066 --> 01:28:03,200
Kuingin kau melindungiku.

1113
01:28:03,200 --> 01:28:04,666
Tidak bos, tak bisa pakai senjata.

1114
01:28:04,666 --> 01:28:07,266
Ya, kau bisa.
Kita sambil latihan sekarang.

1115
01:28:08,566 --> 01:28:10,800
Apa yang kau lihat?
/ Belum ada.

1116
01:28:10,933 --> 01:28:13,266
Galilah pelan-pelan area situ.

1117
01:28:13,700 --> 01:28:16,566
Pelan.
/ Kulihat kotak plastik kuning.

1118
01:28:16,566 --> 01:28:19,466
Sekitar situ mungkin ada kabel
atau detonator.

1119
01:28:21,700 --> 01:28:22,966
Hati-hati.

1120
01:28:25,266 --> 01:28:27,333
Ini granat!
/ Baik.

1121
01:28:27,333 --> 01:28:28,466
Jangan pegang itu.

1122
01:28:28,466 --> 01:28:30,266
Kau lihat kabel atau detonator?

1123
01:28:30,266 --> 01:28:30,700
Ya,

1124
01:28:30,700 --> 01:28:33,200
kulihat kabelnya.
/ Arahkan lagi padaku.

1125
01:28:37,166 --> 01:28:37,966
Ya Tuhan.

1126
01:28:38,866 --> 01:28:40,833
Aku tak bisa.
/ Lihat aku.

1127
01:28:41,100 --> 01:28:42,466
Kita bisa lakukan ini sama-sama.

1128
01:28:42,466 --> 01:28:43,566
Abaikan yang di sana.

1129
01:28:43,566 --> 01:28:45,666
Ceritakan soal bosmu.
/ Persetan orang itu!

1130
01:28:45,666 --> 01:28:48,133
Dia berhutang padaku,
dan dia harus melunasinya.

1131
01:28:48,133 --> 01:28:50,100
Aku yang berhutang padamu,
jika kau selesaikan ini, kawan.

1132
01:28:50,100 --> 01:28:52,300
Lalu kita balas dia.

1133
01:28:54,466 --> 01:28:55,666
Mengapa kau disini/

1134
01:28:55,666 --> 01:28:57,500
Penjinak bom Tentara Inggris.

1135
01:28:57,500 --> 01:28:58,366
Kau melewatkan satu.

1136
01:28:58,366 --> 01:29:00,366
Lucu, hey.

1137
01:29:00,366 --> 01:29:01,766
Apa mau kita keluar dari sini?

1138
01:29:02,066 --> 01:29:03,100
Kalau begitu, ayo mulai.

1139
01:29:03,100 --> 01:29:04,166
Ya.

1140
01:29:04,166 --> 01:29:06,400
Rahim, lindungi dia.

1141
01:29:08,166 --> 01:29:10,100
Kulihat tabung plastik dilakban.

1142
01:29:10,100 --> 01:29:13,300
Itu detonator,
potong kabelnya satu-satu.

1143
01:29:21,866 --> 01:29:22,666
Sebentar.

1144
01:29:24,600 --> 01:29:26,166
Bos, amunisiku habis.

1145
01:29:30,166 --> 01:29:31,433
Potong yang satunya lagi.

1146
01:29:48,100 --> 01:29:49,300
Oh, sialan.

1147
01:29:53,600 --> 01:29:55,400
Rahim, kita aman?

1148
01:29:55,424 --> 01:29:57,332
Aman.

1149
01:29:57,333 --> 01:29:58,266
Karalis?

1150
01:30:04,000 --> 01:30:07,600
Aku menyukaimu.
Kuingin lihat batu permatanya, seksi.

1151
01:30:07,700 --> 01:30:09,400
Ayo.

1152
01:30:12,866 --> 01:30:13,666
Rahim!

1153
01:30:23,490 --> 01:30:28,490
<i>Karalis mewujudkan cita-cita masa kecilnya
dengan membeli cagar alam di Afrika Tengah.</i>

1154
01:30:28,514 --> 01:30:32,414
<i>Survei geologi menunjukkan
potensi penambangan berlian.</i>

1155
01:30:32,438 --> 01:30:36,438
<i>Baru-baru ini dia naik peringkat ke 20
Buronan Interpol yang Paling Dicari.</i>

1156
01:30:36,462 --> 01:30:41,462
<i>Rahim membangun kompleks multi-keluarga
dan mendirikan perusahaan sendiri.</i>

1157
01:30:41,486 --> 01:30:48,486
<i>Ayahnya terus menanyakan asal uang itu
dan mengapa mereka mengganti nama marga keluarga.</i>

1158
01:30:48,510 --> 01:30:52,210
<i>Mayor Will "The Thrill" Tranter
menghabiskan $30 juta untuk kokain dan melacur.</i>

1159
01:30:52,234 --> 01:30:54,434
<i>Cuma bercanda.</i>

1160
01:30:54,458 --> 01:30:57,458
<i>Donasi anonim sebesar 25 juta dolar AS
diberikan kepada F.U.Z.E.,</i>

1161
01:30:57,459 --> 01:31:01,459
<i>sebuah badan amal yang berdedikasi untuk membersihkan
